name: Front Lever
description: A foundational straight-arm strength hold where the body is parallel to the ground.

name: Tuck Front Lever
description: A beginner progression for the front lever with knees tucked to the chest.

name: Advanced Tuck Front Lever
description: A progression where the torso is more parallel to the ground than the tuck hold.

name: Muscle-up
description: An advanced transition from a pull-up to a dip.
